Administrative Assistant x 2 (1 Contract/1 Perm) (REG/201404/05/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00007581
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Apr 24 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Organize, coordinate and support business meetings, conferences and trainings for business units.
Arrange travel logistics including ticket, visa application, hotel arrangement and travel movement list, etc. for Business Unit employees.
Provide general office administration supports to Business Unit employees including but not limited to checking incoming order mailbox, reports preparation, schedule updating and sales tender document etc.
Assist workshop, project and operation team to raise non-inventory purchase order.
Support all administration work for Gul Road Regulator Workshop and Store including purchasing of control of workshop expendables such as uniforms, gloves, safety shoes etc.
Raise e-form for necessary network and sharefolder access.
Ensure cubicle ready for new joiners; prepare name card, name badge, computer equipment and mobile phone etc.
Collect all the company assets and return to Executive Assistant for record.
Requirements:
Diploma/Degree in Business or related discipline with 7 years of administrative or relevant experience.
High degree of initiative and good organization skills.
Ability to communicate and interact with people at all levels and work independently with minimal supervision.
Tact in dealing with internal and external customers and vendors phone calls.
Proficient in Microsoft Office application software.